<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٢٤٢ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بَشَّارٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1358">حَرَمِيٌّ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>قَالَ: أَخْبَرَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4623">عُمَارَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4458">عِكْرِمَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span> قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«لَمَّا فُتِحَتْ خَيْبَرُ قُلْنَا: الْآنَ نَشْبَعُ مِنَ التَّمْرِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>